{"word":"Amen","slug":"amen","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Amen</b> A word used to reinforce a statement<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=5&verse=22'>Num 5:22</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=27&verse=26'>Deu 27:26</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=5&verse=13'>Neh 5:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=47&chapter=1&verse=20'>2Co 1:20</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=66&chapter=1&verse=18'>Rev 1:18</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=66&chapter=22&verse=20'>Rev 22:20</a><br/> Used in prayer<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=1&verse=36'>1Ki 1:36</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=16&verse=36'>1Ch 16:36</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=8&verse=6'>Neh 8:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=41&verse=13'>Psa 41:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=72&verse=19'>Psa 72:19</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=89&verse=52'>Psa 89:52</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=106&verse=48'>Psa 106:48</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=28&verse=6'>Jer 28:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=6&verse=13'>Mat 6:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=46&chapter=14&verse=16'>1Co 14:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=66&chapter=5&verse=14'>Rev 5:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=66&chapter=19&verse=4'>Rev 19:4</a><br/> A title of Christ<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=66&chapter=3&verse=14'>Rev 3:14</a>"}]}